{"id":587793,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/06/【立此存照】山东某中学下发雷人阅读材料-宣扬汉/","date":"2018-06-27T11:58:59Z","modified":"2018-06-27T11:58:59Z","title":"【立此存照】山东某中学下发雷人阅读材料 宣扬汉族至上主义","content":"<p><strong>【编者注】近日有</strong>网友曝光，山东省诸城第一中学给学生下发了一份雷人的阅读材料。材料内容来自一个叫“至道学宫”的栏目，创立者自称为“正本清源”，要复兴弘扬“正统的华夏思想和文化”。这种糅合了汉族至上主义、传统糟粕和毛左言论的“学说”，似乎&#8230;&#8230;<a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/question/61824705\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">颇有市场</a>。</p>\n<blockquote><p><a href=\"https://weibo.com/3232351640/GnhvZENkr\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">@一朵花巫</a>:<br />\n我们学校发这种材料[微笑]<br />\n是想搞事情吗[微笑]<br />\n肠胃不适[微笑] ​​​​</p></blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/c0a9c598ly1fspl7pakxej21f90djgst.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-587796\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/c0a9c598ly1fspl7pakxej21f90djgst.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"158\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/c0a9c598ly1fspl7pakxej21f90djgst.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/c0a9c598ly1fspl7pakxej21f90djgst-300x79.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/c0a9c598ly1fspl7pakxej21f90djgst-768x203.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>我们华夏文化，是天道-圣人-百姓这个结构。[&#8230;]印度要饭文化的结构更有意思，[&#8230;]这是一种动物园结构的文化，类似于大猩猩-小猩猩-饲养员结构。</p></blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/c0a9c598ly1fspl7pkotpj21hr081jw7.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-587797\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/c0a9c598ly1fspl7pkotpj21hr081jw7.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"90\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/c0a9c598ly1fspl7pkotpj21hr081jw7.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/c0a9c598ly1fspl7pkotpj21hr081jw7-300x45.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/c0a9c598ly1fspl7pkotpj21hr081jw7-768x115.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>[&#8230;]所谓的欧洲文艺复兴不过就是一群猥琐的色情美术工作者，画一些伤风败俗的光屁股女人，来取悦一些低级趣味的商人罢了。[&#8230;]</p></blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/c0a9c598ly1fspl7pqfr8j21hq070jvn.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-587798\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/c0a9c598ly1fspl7pqfr8j21hq070jvn.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"78\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/c0a9c598ly1fspl7pqfr8j21hq070jvn.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/c0a9c598ly1fspl7pqfr8j21hq070jvn-300x39.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/c0a9c598ly1fspl7pqfr8j21hq070jvn-768x100.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/c0a9c598ly1fspl7pqfr8j21hq070jvn-220x30.jpg 220w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>[&#8230;]我们作为一个大国，一个要向世界立万世垂范的大国，怎么可以向这两个小小的殖民地和文化糟粕集散地进口文化呢？[&#8230;]</p></blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/c0a9c598ly1fspl7pwcuij21hs06x77e.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-587799\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/c0a9c598ly1fspl7pwcuij21hs06x77e.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"77\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/c0a9c598ly1fspl7pwcuij21hs06x77e.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/c0a9c598ly1fspl7pwcuij21hs06x77e-300x39.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/c0a9c598ly1fspl7pwcuij21hs06x77e-768x99.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/c0a9c598ly1fspl8jes2uj216o0f8h6h.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-587803\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/c0a9c598ly1fspl8jes2uj216o0f8h6h.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"214\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/c0a9c598ly1fspl8jes2uj216o0f8h6h.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/c0a9c598ly1fspl8jes2uj216o0f8h6h-300x107.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/c0a9c598ly1fspl8jes2uj216o0f8h6h-768x274.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>[&#8230;]天地之间，以人最贵，所以毛圣人处处维护人民的利益，禁止各种害人虫复辟，伤害百姓。</p></blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/c0a9c598ly1fspl7ojasfj21hs0jzwpo.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-587795\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/c0a9c598ly1fspl7ojasfj21hs0jzwpo.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"223\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/c0a9c598ly1fspl7ojasfj21hs0jzwpo.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/c0a9c598ly1fspl7ojasfj21hs0jzwpo-300x111.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/c0a9c598ly1fspl7ojasfj21hs0jzwpo-768x285.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>接下来的新潮流，就是再一次的以夏变夷，推翻跨国金融奴隶制，推动地球走向大统一。[&#8230;]毛圣人开启了以夏变夷的大历史，一个地球版的秦始皇，相信不远的将来就会降临。这是这个星球上，前所未有的最伟大最壮丽的事业。而这个事业的起点，就是让更多的黄皮肤夷狄，回归华夏文明，种族苏醒、文化苏醒、道德苏醒，越来越多的华夏人苏醒[&#8230;]</p></blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/c0a9c598ly1fspl7qp1awj21gy0afjwi.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-587800\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/c0a9c598ly1fspl7qp1awj21gy0afjwi.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"118\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/c0a9c598ly1fspl7qp1awj21gy0afjwi.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/c0a9c598ly1fspl7qp1awj21gy0afjwi-300x59.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/c0a9c598ly1fspl7qp1awj21gy0afjwi-768x151.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>那些所谓的丁克，不婚族，同性恋，以及各种所谓有信仰的精神变态者，都是以邪辟之理修身所造成的身心病态，这些都不适什么时髦，而是身心疾病。[&#8230;]这些人，因为修身不正，所以才会被天刑戮[&#8230;]</p></blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/c0a9c598ly1fspl7qzk87j21hr07178k.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-587801\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/c0a9c598ly1fspl7qzk87j21hr07178k.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"79\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/c0a9c598ly1fspl7qzk87j21hr07178k.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/c0a9c598ly1fspl7qzk87j21hr07178k-300x39.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/c0a9c598ly1fspl7qzk87j21hr07178k-768x101.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/c0a9c598ly1fspl7qzk87j21hr07178k-220x30.jpg 220w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>所以家庭存在的目的，不是为了给爱情建造一座房子，而是为了生儿育女。[&#8230;]</p></blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/c0a9c598ly1fspl7y5zwij21gv0ch79d.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-587802\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/c0a9c598ly1fspl7y5zwij21gv0ch79d.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"142\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/c0a9c598ly1fspl7y5zwij21gv0ch79d.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/c0a9c598ly1fspl7y5zwij21gv0ch79d-300x71.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/c0a9c598ly1fspl7y5zwij21gv0ch79d-768x182.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>[&#8230;]至道学宫的每一个读者，在这一分钟，在心智上，都已经超越了历史上所有西方哲学家们的总和。[&#8230;]所谓的哲学，就是蠢人们为了美化他们的愚昧，故意发明出来的智力装饰，[&#8230;]</p></blockquote>\n<p><strong>以下评论由数字时代编辑收集自新浪微博：</strong></p>\n<p>@我讲旧常识:回复@一朵花巫: 转。看介绍还是个高考成绩不错的重点中学。不敢想象穷乡僻壤小学校是怎样。</p>\n<p>@少女大师姊：想起今天早些时候在其他地方看到的这条言论👉<br />\n<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/006pzzARly1fspvawm4lvj30lb024wf4.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-587809\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/006pzzARly1fspvawm4lvj30lb024wf4.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"440\" height=\"44\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/006pzzARly1fspvawm4lvj30lb024wf4.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/006pzzARly1fspvawm4lvj30lb024wf4-300x30.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" /></a></p>\n<p>@Wolfurrr：能这么全方位的、反智 歧视 自负 等等把几乎所有的雷点全戳爆也是很厉害………………好奇一下标题是啥？</p>\n<p>@老佛林特船长：我勒个去。大局观省已经成这样了吗？？</p>\n<p>@Graf_FrostFuchs：这是谁把清朝考了一辈子都没中举的穷秀才挖出来了？</p>\n<p>@李吱吱·：领导层的清辫子还没剪吗</p>\n<p>@北国佳人李春姬:罢黜百家 独尊乳术</p>\n<p>@Jung206：这是什么邪教啊！！！！太可怕了</p>\n","author":980,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,27949],"tags":[10755,13379,31267,8646]}